     H            Y.
     F** AJER08 ****************************************
     F* ..  MENU M/F IS CANCELLED BY  MENU UNIT  *
     F* I-HASADA                        87.07.26       *
     F**************************************** AJER08 **
     FAJEPW08 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FEGBPL12 UF  E           K        DISK
     FRGAPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     E                    ER      1   4 60               ERROR MSG
     I            DS
     I                                        1  10 UUSER
     I                                        1   2 UUS2
     I                                        1   7 UANT7
     I                                       11  20 TANT
     I                                       11  12 TAN2
     I                                       11  17 TANT7
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PUSER  10
     C                     MOVE PUSER     UUSER
     C           STEP1     TAG
     C                     EXFMTAJEPW081
     C   KA                GOTO END
     C                     SETOF                     99
     C           TANT      COMP *BLANK                   9901
     C   99                MOVE ER,1      MSG
     C   99                GOTO STEP1
     C           TANT7     IFNE 'QSECOFR'
     C           TANT7     IFNE 'QSYSOPR'
     C           TANT7     IFNE 'QPGMR  '
     C           TANT      CHAINRGAPL111             99
     C   99                MOVE ER,2      MSG
     C   99                GOTO STEP1
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C           UUS2      COMP TAN2                 9999
     C           *IN99     IFEQ '1'
     C           UANT7     IFNE 'QPGMR  '
     C           UUS2      ANDNE'I0'
     C                     MOVE ER,3      MSG
     C                     GOTO STEP1
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C           UMNO      COMP '00'                   99
     C   99                MOVE ER,4      MSG
     C   99                GOTO STEP1
     C           *INKE     CABEQ'0'       STEP1
     C           MKEY      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           WTANT
     C                     KFLD           WMENU
     C                     KFLD           WMDAN
     C                     MOVE TANT      WTANT  10
     C                     MOVE UMNO      WMENU   20
     C                     Z-ADD0         WMDAN   10
     C                     SETON                     02
     C                     Z-ADD0         ICTR    30
     C                     MOVEL'MENU'    OMENU   6
     C                     MOVE UMNO      OMENU
     C           MKEY      SETLLEGBPL121
     C           STEP2     TAG
     C                     READ EGBPL121                 01
     C   01                GOTO STEP1
     C           WTANT     CABNEM1USRC    STEP1
     C           WMENU     CABNEM1MNNO    STEP1
     C                     MOVE 'D'       M1SKJY
     C                     DELETEGBPL121
     C           ICTR      ADD  1         ICTR
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C           END       TAG
     C                     SETON                     LR
**
E-01 TEAM MEMBER NO. ISN'T INPUT
E-02 TEAM MEMBER NO. INPUT INTO ISN'T USED CURRENTLY
E-03 I CAN'T APPOINT TEAM MEMBER NO. OF ANOTHER DEPARTMENT
E-04 MENU NAME IS NOT RANGE FROM 00 TO 99
